sources.modules/header/header.sass:
//header-----------------------------------------	
.header_style
	background-color: #FFFFFF
	width: 100%
	height: 70px
	box-shadow: 0px 10px 20px rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.05)
	display: flex
	flex-direction: row
	align-items: center
	justify-content: space-between
//------------------------------------------------------



//–õ–æ–≥–æ—Ç–∏–ø------------------------------------------------
.header-logo
	margin: 15px 0px 15px 90px
//-------------------------------------------------------



//–ì–æ—Ä–∏–∑–æ–Ω—Ç–∞–ª—å–Ω–æ–µ –º–µ–Ω—é —Å—Å—ã–ª–æ–∫------------------------------
.header-menu 
	min-width: 450px
	width: 527px
	display: flex
	justify-content: space-between
	margin: 26px 0 26px 300px
	font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif
	font-size: 14px
	line-height: 17px
	color: rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.5)

.header-menu__item_home
	font-weight: bold

.header-menu__item_services-icon
	padding-left: 3px

nav.header-menu a, div.header-buttons a
	text-decoration: none 
	color: rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.5)

a:active
	color: rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.75)
//---------------------------------------------------------



//–í—Ö–æ–¥, —Ä–µ–≥–∏—Å—Ç—Ä–∞—Ü–∏—è----------------------------------------
.header-buttons
	min-width: 180px
	width: 200px
	margin: auto auto auto 25px
	font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif
	font-style: normal
	font-weight: bold
	font-size: 12px
	line-height: 15px
	display: flex
	justify-content: space-between

.header-buttons__login
	padding: 9px 20px 10px 20px
	border: 2px solid #BC9CFF
	border-radius: 22px
	color: #BC9CFF
	
.header-buttons__register
	padding: 9px 20px 10px 20px
	border: 2px solid #BC9CFF
	border-radius: 22px
	color: #FFFFFF
	background: linear-gradient(180deg, #BC9CFF 0%, #8BA4F9 100%)
//---------------------------------------------------------------------

sources.modules/diagram/diagram.sass:
//–ë–ª–æ–∫ –¥–∏–∞–≥—Ä–∞–º–º—ã====================
div.wrap
  position: absolute
  width: 300px
  height: 300px
 
  //–ó–Ω–∞—á–µ–Ω–∏—è========================
  div.container
    width: 120px
    height: 120px
    overflow: hidden
    border-radius: 50%
    position: relative

    //–ü–µ—Ä–≤—ã–π —Å–µ–∫—Ç–æ—Ä===================
    div.sector
      width: 50%
      height: 50%
      position: absolute
      left: 50.5%
      top: 0
      transform-origin: right top
      background: #BC9CFF

    //–í—Ç–æ—Ä–æ–π —Å–µ–∫—Ç–æ—Ä==================
    div.test
      width: 50%
      height: 50%
      position: absolute
      left: 51%
      top: 51%
      transform-origin: right top
      background: #6FCF97

    //–¢—Ä–µ—Ç–∏–π —Å–µ–∫—Ç–æ—Ä==================
    div.test2
      width: 50%
      height: 100%
      position: absolute
      left: -0.5%
      top: 0
      transform-origin: left top
      background: #FFE39C

  //–ë–µ–ª—ã–π —Ñ–æ–Ω========================
  .container:after
    content: ''
    position: absolute
    width: 94%
    height: 94%
    background: white
    border-radius: 50%
    top: 3%
    left: 3%

  //–®–∏—Ä–æ–∫–∞—è –ø–æ–ª–æ—Å–∞===================
  div.container2
    width: 120px
    height: 120px
    overflow: hidden
    border-radius: 50%
    position: relative
    top: -120px

    //–í—ã–¥–µ–ª–µ–Ω–Ω—ã–π —Å–µ–∫—Ç–æ—Ä===============
    div.sector2
      width: 50%
      height: 50%
      position: absolute
      left: 50.5%
      top: 0
      transform-origin: right top
      background: #BC9CFF

  //–ë–µ–ª—ã–π —Ñ–æ–Ω –¥–ª—è –≤—ã–¥–µ–ª–µ–Ω–∏—è===========
  .container2:after
    content: ''
    position: absolute
    width: 84%
    height: 84%
    background: white
    border-radius: 50%
    top: 8%
    left: 8%

  //–¢–µ–∫—Å—Ç===================================    
  div.text
    position: absolute
    left: 10%
    top: 12%
    display: flex
    align-items: center
    flex-flow: column nowrap

    //–ó–∞–≥–æ–ª–æ–≤–æ–∫==============================
    span.header
      font-family: 'Quicksand', sans-serif
      font-style: normal
      font-weight: bold
      font-size: 24px
      line-height: 30px
      display: flex
      align-items: center
      text-align: center
      color: #BC9CFF

    //–¢–µ–∫—Å—Ç –ø–æ–¥ –∑–∞–≥–æ–ª–æ–≤–∫–æ–º====================
    span.text
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif
      font-style: normal
      font-weight: bold
      font-size: 12px
      line-height: 15px
      text-transform: uppercase
      color: #BC9CFF

sources.modules/reserv/reserv.sass:
//–í–µ–± —Ñ–æ—Ä–º–∞--------------------------------------------
#reserve-header__rubsimv
	font-family: 'PT Sans', serif

.reserv
	width: 380px
	height: 511px
	background: #FFFFFF
	border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12)
	box-sizing: border-box
	box-shadow: 0px 0px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2)
	border-radius: 4px

.reserv-wrap
	display: flex
	flex-flow: column nowrap
	justify-content: space-between
	align-items: flex-start
	margin: 40px 30px
	height: 441px
	width: 320px

//----------------------------------------------------


//–∑–∞–≥–æ–ª–æ–≤–æ–∫-------------------------------------------
.reserve-header
	display: flex
	flex-flow: row nowrap
	justify-content: space-between
	align-items: center
	height: 30px
	width: 320px

.header__numroom
	font-family: 'Quicksand', sans-serif
	font-style: normal
	font-weight: bold
	font-size: 14px
	line-height: 17px
	/* Dark 100% */
	color: #1F2041

div.reserve-header span.header__numroom_number
	font-family: 'Quicksand', sans-serif
	font-weight: bold
	font-size: 24px
	//line-height: 30px
	color: #1F2041

div.reserve-header span.header__numroom_class
	font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif
	font-style: normal
	font-weight: bold
	font-size: 12px
	line-height: 15px
	/* identical to box height */
	text-transform: uppercase
	/* Primary Color */
	color: #BC9CFF

.header__numroom_second
	font-family: Montserrat
	font-style: normal
	font-weight: bold
	font-size: 14px
	line-height: 18px
	/* or 129% */
	color: rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.5)

//----------------------------------------------------



//–≤—ã–±–æ—Ä –¥–∞—Ç ----------------------------------------------
.reserve-dates
	display: flex
	flex-flow: row nowrap
	justify-content: space-between
	font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif
	font-style: normal
	font-weight: bold
	font-size: 12px
	line-height: 15px
	text-transform: uppercase
	color: #1F2041
	margin-top: 8px

.reserve-arrival,.reserve-checkout
	display: flex
	flex-flow: column wrap
	align-content: flex-start
	font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif
	margin-right: 20px

.reserve-arrival__header,.reserve-checkout__header,.reserve-guests__header
	font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif
	font-weight: bold
	font-size: 12px
	line-height: 15px
	text-transform: uppercase
	color: #1F2041
	margin-bottom: 5px
	
.reserve-arrival__input,.reserve-checkout__input
	border: none 
	outline: none 
	-webkit-appearance: none 
	background: #FFFFFF
	border: 1px solid rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.25)
	box-sizing: border-box
	border-radius: 4px
	color: rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.75)
	width: 150px
	height: 44px
	padding-left: 8px
	font-size: 14px
	background: url(modules/reserv/img/expand.png) no-repeat 90% 60%
	font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif
	font-style: normal
	font-weight: normal
	font-size: 14px
	line-height: 24px
	color: rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.75)

//----------------------------------------------------



//–ö–æ–ª–∏—á–µ—Å—Ç–≤–æ –≥–æ—Å—Ç–µ–π-------------------------------------------
.reserve-guests
	margin-top: 10px

.reserve-guests__input
	width: 306px
	height: 38px
	border: none 
	outline: none 
	-webkit-appearance: none 
	background: #FFFFFF
	border: 1px solid rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.25)
	box-sizing: border-box
	border-radius: 4px
	color: rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.75)
	text-align: left
	background: url(modules/reserv/img/expand.png) no-repeat 96% 50%
	font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif
	font-style: normal
	font-weight: normal
	font-size: 14px
	line-height: 24px
	color: rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.75)
	cursor: pointer

//----------------------------------------------------



//–¢–∞–±–ª–∏—Ü–∞ —Ä–∞—Å—á–µ—Ç–æ–≤ —Å—Ç–æ–∏–º–æ—Å—Ç–∏----------------------------------------------------
.reserve-price 
	width: 100%
	height: 110px
	display: flex
	justify-content: space-between
	align-items: flex-start
	flex-flow: column nowrap
	margin-top: 22px

.price-table__row
	width: 100%
	display: flex
	flex-flow: row nowrap
	justify-content: space-between
	align-items: flex-start
	font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif
	font-style: normal
	font-weight: normal
	font-size: 14px
	line-height: 24px
	color: rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.75)
	position: relative


div.price-table__cell //–ö–æ—Å—Ç—ã–ª—å –¥–ª—è –ø–µ—Ä–µ–Ω–æ—Å–∞ —Å–ª–æ–≤–∞ –Ω–∞ –≤—Ç–æ—Ä—É—é —Å—Ç—Ä–æ–∫—É
	width: 200px
	height: 40px
	display: flex
	flex-flow: row wrap
	line-height: 20px

span.price-table__attention
	position: absolute
	right: 23%
	width: 23px
	height: 20px
	text-align: center
	color: rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.25)
	padding-bottom: 2px
	border: 1px solid rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.25)
	border-radius: 100%
	margin-left: 5px

//----------------------------------------------------



//Total Price-----------------------------------------
.reserve-total_price
	display: flex
	flex-flow: row nowrap
	justify-content: space-between
	width: 100%
	font-family: 'Quicksand', sans-serif
	font-style: normal
	font-weight: bold
	font-size: 19px
	line-height: 24px
	color: #1F2041
	margin-top: 25px

.total_price__border
	width: 60%
	border-bottom: 1px dashed rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.25)

//----------------------------------------------------



//–ë—Ä–æ–Ω–∏—Ä–æ–≤–∞–Ω–∏–µ-------------------------------------------
.reserve-button_wrap
	display: flex
	flex-flow: row nowrap
	position: relative
	margin-top: 21px

.reserve-pay__button
	border: none 
	outline: none 
	-webkit-appearance: none 
	background: linear-gradient(180deg, #BC9CFF 0%, #8BA4F9 100%)
	border-radius: 22px
	width: 320px
	height: 44px
	font-family: Montserrat
	font-style: normal
	font-weight: bold
	font-size: 12px
	line-height: 15px
	text-align: center
	text-transform: uppercase
	color: #FFFFFF
	

.reserve-pay__img
	position: absolute
	top: 30%
	right: 5%

//----------------------------------------------------
